window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"If we women are really weak then why do they need to discharge so many sperms for one ovum?\" <br>- Pallavi, 27, single, Kingfisher Airlines. </p><p>\"Half the headaches in a man's life involve a woman, and half the heartaches in a woman's life are because of a man.\" <br>- Swadha, 24, single, NH Consultants Pvt. Ltd. </p><p>And then they met him...exactly when they shouldn't have. </p>"; 
